Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:12.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:16.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:24.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:34.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:41.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:48.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set \Nsail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:55.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:59.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:03.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:07.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:10.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:21.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:25.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:32.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:36.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:02:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Round 1! One Lap of the Donut Race"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten us into a real mess, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we gotta do is win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You forgot somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write down your rosters and\Ngive them to our party organizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Members can participate only twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've chosen\Nyour roster, it's set in stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The events of the contest are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A race, a ball game, and a team competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? The race is open to all members,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ball game is open to three,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand the team competition is open to five...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna do all three!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules say that isn't allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what if we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they'll want Captain Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I bet it'll be me. Because I'm cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll now announce the rosters\Nsubmitted by both teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First is the Straw Hat team!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Participating in Round #1's Donut Race is...\Nthe entire Straw Hat crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my "Can't Be in a Race"\Ndisease is kicking in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna do it either,\Nyou know! Just accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Participating in Round #2's Groggy Ring is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Roronoa Zoro, Sanji, \Nand Tony Tony Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't go slowin' me down!\N--That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... gonna try my very... hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Participating in Round #3's\NRun Around Roller is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Luffy,\NNico Robin, Nami, and Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only four people? We're one short.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A captain, a swordsman, \Na navigator, a sniper,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a cook, a doctor, and an archaeologist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then. Who shall I take first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'd have to be that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want that member!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:04:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's finally time\Nfor the merciless Davy Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner gets a feast,\Nwhile the loser gets fleeced!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Itomimizu, the Foxy \NPirates' party organizer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be your commentator \Nfor this competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is Round #1, the Donut Race!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shall we team up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering that some of us\Nhave Devil Fruit powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we should split into two\Nteams of three and four people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boats for the Donut Race can only be made
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from two oars and three empty barrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use of any other materials\Nmeans instant disqualification!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a chance for\Nshipwrights to show their stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those without empty barrels, come get some!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give 'em to you for free!\NWe're generous like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure we can use three barrels\Nto build a boat for four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, three teams it is. \NThey'll consist of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't go busting 'em up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch! I'm gonna make an awesome boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! While everyone's\Nbusy with their boats,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain how the race works!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The course will be one lap\Naround Long Ring Long Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might sound easy, but it's anything but!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A team is immediately out of\Nthe race should their boat sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, all weapons are allowed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even guns, cannons, explosives,\Ncutlasses or anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever complains about unfairness\Nwill be shamed as a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Managed to finish it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is nearly up! Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The final odds are in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll list them in order of popularity,\Nstarting with the most popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The top spot obviously goes to our idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the member of the powerful\NTeam Foxy: Porche-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her is the swordfish fishman\NCapote and the star shark Monda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're riding in the Cutie Wagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a cinch! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! You're using a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rule against fish, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second most popular is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This is unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat team of Navigator Nami,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniper Usopp, and Archeologist Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be riding the Barrel Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That orange-haired chick is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want that dark-haired girl on our crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't need that other guy!\N--Yeah. Never mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Looks like the rowdy Foxy Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhave a soft spot for cutey-pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What lechers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you sure this won't sink?!\N--I already told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still beats those.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't a boat! It's just some scrap wood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So you do that the whole time?\N--Yep! I just keep running really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle they even float...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's up to us if we\Ndon't wanna lose this race...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third most popular is the Harem Nocturne,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boat of the beautiful,\Nby the beautiful, for the beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fourth place is the Crab Crane,\Na regular in the top ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fifth and sixth place are\Nthe Swordfish King #1 and #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventh most popular is the\Nparty-loving Pleasure Boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In eighth place is the Duke Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What about our boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Mine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor Chopper and Swordsman\NZoro's Basically Barrels is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...third from last!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the It's a Raft...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wins the booby prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Means we're second to last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there's an even worse boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the very last place\Ngoes to the giant boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Mothership Coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think oars are long\Nenough for that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it even move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, oars are too short for this boat!\NIt's filled with seawater, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many barrels did they use, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing is just three giant barrels,\Nall stuck together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't breaking any rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! All the boats are at the starting line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be providing commentary during the race
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:09:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from atop Chirp-Chirp, a rare\NSouth Blue Super Sparrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porche-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you sink, nose dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to win now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sinking opponents is fair game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Listen to that crazy talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let 'em talk, Porche-chan.\NWe'll sink 'em in three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Monda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we even have a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Usopp! Anything happens\Nto the ladies and I'll filet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! No one's ever beat us\Nin an orthodox-rules game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think this race will last \Nfive minutes, Hamburg?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take these Eternal Poses\Nso that you don't get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to leave the island and go too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the island? Why would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking the shortest route,\Nalong the inside track!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't think it'll be that simple...\N--Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that gigantic one in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all their other boats are on the\Noutside track, facing outward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious, don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! On your marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't it be so simple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just trust me! Men! Leave the\Nshore as soon as we start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?!\N--Grin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donut!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I've got a bad feeling about this!\N--Tell us why!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Push it! Push it! Push it!\N--Push it! Push it! Push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna teach ya what \Nthis boat exists for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! We're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami! Don't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there they are! The Mothership\NCoaster's infamous Barrel Mines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sink right away, though!\NGive us some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go away!\N--Stupid things! I'm gonna send you flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop, Luffy.\N--Yeah! They'll explode like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just gotta get rid of 'em\Nwithout touching 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand me that oar, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Robin-chan! Hold on\Nto your boat! Ride the wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't ride that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! This is neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! We're breaking apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold water...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The Straw Hat teams are\Nspeeding to the front of the pack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! They're going to catch up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Monda! Give it \Neverything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us backup, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally calmed down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. The shock busted \Nthe raft a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that was fun! I hope\Nthere's another wave! Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?! We will sink next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:14:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope the girls are \Nokay... There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Welcome!\N--Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't be so cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make yourselves comfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some inari sushi and\Nkitsune udon! No charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?! Thanks! Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd love to have a cook like you join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your twirly eyebrow's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Maybe I should be Davy Backed right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentleman in the fur coat--\Nyou must be exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a fur coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now! I have just the thing for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does a candy apple sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! Is it sweet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Some more drinks over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Pleasure Boat and Harem\NNocturne unleash their secret move:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Party Distraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Straw Hat boats have been KOed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! Seconds, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow, this is sweet! You jerk!\N--Whoa, you're really chowin' down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your beard's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Get back to the race!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be concerned\Nabout others right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to focus on yourselves first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capote! Give 'em a taste\Nof your Fishman Karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Surface Splitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boat's come apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls are in trouble! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper! Let's go!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san! Robin-chan! I'll save you!\N--Forget those floozies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--Come back, Twirly Eyebrow Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our balance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Flame Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocho Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?!\N--Capote!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, swim and pull the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capote! Monda! Pull yourselves together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paddle! Paddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Currently in the lead\Nis the adorable Cutie Wagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In second is the Barrel Tiger, followed by--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? When did they get back into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Followed by the Crab Crane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get to it, Hamburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It's finally time, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Robin-chan! I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Get me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This thing's fast!\N--Yeah, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:17:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Nami-san! Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gettin' nowhere like this.\NWouldn't it be faster just to paddle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... But we used the oars for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a "hello," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. This is just our style.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That so? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We're taking you down with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Basically Barrels and\NSwordfish King #1 and #2 have sunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, they're out of the race!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're out of the race...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's up to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Usopp! Use a dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll use this Breath Dial to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paddling would be faster than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we use up all the wind\Nescaping from Navarone Fortress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't you have a Jet Dial?!\N--Those are impossible to get!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about an Impact Dial?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I left it on the Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! You don't believe me?!\NWhy would I lie about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our crew members is on the line here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we end up losing,\Nthey'll definitely take me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:19:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen! I'm too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish. Now just paddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This is no time for reading, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm paddling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are, but you\Ndon't seem like you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll end up like me if \Nyou don't work hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly savvy about the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we head straight for the goal,\Nor shall we sink them instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoy the occasional leisurely\Ntrip across the goal line,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wanna make that chick pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winning isn't enough for me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The race has entered its climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cutie Wagon remains in the lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,followed by the Barrel Tiger\Nand the Crab Crane in third!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd the Crab Crane go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Those guys' kicks were insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! The Crab Crane is out\Nof the race! When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely rendezvous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How are they going so fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Screw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out... of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he was in the water too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We better get paddling\Nor this'll all go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you did, but we won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! We just passed them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get close to us again--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How is this?\N--Wonderful, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They already caught on. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capote!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Can you try it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he'll be much help for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just keep moving!\NWe can't let 'em get a bigger lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll sink them after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up ahead are the biggest obstacles\Nof the course: the Long Coral Reef
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Long Ring Whirlpool\Nof Long Cape beyond it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will they overcome these?! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Full Dash" Hamburg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atop him, making an appearance at last,\Nis the Master of Obstruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great scoundrel who\Nhates fairness: our boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Silver Fox" Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got an evil idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:09.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:12.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:18.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:20.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:23.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:29.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:32.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:34.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:37.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless \Nsky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:41.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:43.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:46.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:52.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:55.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:57.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:00.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:08.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many idiots! I'll be too embarrassed\Nto live if we lose to these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.67,0:23:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll take our crew, too!\NThat's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna lose if we don't do\Nsomething! Time for my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! Who's winning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually eaten a--!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--On the next episode of One Piece!\N--Let me finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"'Silver Fox' Foxy! The \NMerciless Interference"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
